p:
Peter Nelson W Smith H Elsner C Whaley G Matteson Charles Lunderblad Dennis Coff and Jasob Anner on oath say eash for himself that he is one of the applisants named in the forgoing eash of their own self that by the same lead knows the contents therof and believe the same
to be true
Petter Nelsson W Smith H Elsner C Whaley G Mattson Charles Lundblad Dennis his X mark Coff
Subscribed and sworn to before me this 3d day of May AD 1875
